P_{n}\pr\pr\left(x_{0}\right)=f\pr\pr\left(x_{0}\right)\\
\tr\\
P_{n}^{\left(n\right)}\left(x_{0}\right)=f^{\left(n\right)}\left(x_{0}\right)
